        " اَلْقَلَنْسُوَةِ اَلسَّوْدَاءِ فَقَالَ «لاَ تُصَلِّ فِيهَا فَإِنَّهَا لِبَاسُ أَهْلِ اَلنَّارِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.766 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) was asked about praying while wearing a black cap.\nImam (as) said: \"Do not pray in it, for it is the attire of the people of the Fire”."
        ]
